aces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0bedda18db929970ca775d20085f898aed663fb","tid":58876,"uid":11248,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T16:00:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>唔知點解我用十人竹水打到喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nBTW 倉頡都幾on9<br />\n麥係十人弓戈<br />\n但係麥字旁係十水</blockquote><br />\n點會呀，麥字邊係 十弓</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nwindows同iOS既倉頡又可能係唔同講法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\niOS打就兩樣都打到 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a23651b400d1d4437abaa306e104eb0bc0a8e4b","tid":58876,"uid":60196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T17:37:34.000Z","msg":"其實倉頡拆碼係有啲bug，睇下三代倉頡同五代就知，例如&ldquo;應&rdquo;字，三代係&ldquo;戈土心&rdquo;，五代係&ldquo;戈人土心&rdquo;；又例如&ldquo;非&rdquo;字三代係&ldquo;中一卜卜卜&rdquo;，五代係&ldquo;中一尸卜&rdquo;。"},{"pid":"8d48c391859f2a80a3545e1f25acae41faf69cdc","tid":58876,"uid":13100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T21:46:31.000Z","msg":"當年1978年作者編碼用嘅係字典<br />\n唔係1983年出版嘅big5字表<br />\n<br />\n撐=手火月手，個「牙」點拆成「手」？<br />\n原因係有「撑」「撐」兩種寫法<br />\n倉頡編碼時用撑<br />\nbig5揀咗撐<br />\n結果就<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n要到unicode年代先將兩隻字分返開<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n第一代big5好煩，好多香港用字都冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}